high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room and turn left to face the end of the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Turn around to face the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the tomato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To cool a tomato slice and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and face the table to your left.
Take the knife off of the table in front of you.
Turn left and face the counter by the stove on your left.
Slice the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Place the knife on the counter in front of you.
Take a tomato slice off of the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave on top of the stove to your left.
Heat up the tomato slice in the microwave in front of you, take the tomato out and close the microwave.
Turn around and face the fridge on your left.
Place the tomato slice in the fridge in front of you and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left then go to the right side of the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Turn left then head to the counter beside the stove
Cut the tomato on the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Pick up a slice of tomato
Turn right then head to the microwave
Open the microwave, put in and out the tomato slice then close microwave
Look down then turn right head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put in the slice of tomato then close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice tomato in the fridge
